Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:04.86,English,,0,0,0,,- Alright, I'm about to go for my first ever ride in a fully autonomous vehicle.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:04.86,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我现在要第一次坐上全自动驾驶的汽车
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.66,0:00:11.62,English,,0,0,0,,Whoa, no driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.66,0:00:11.62,Chinese,,0,0,0,,哇，没有司机
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.14,0:00:14.89,English,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.14,0:00:14.89,Chinese,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.89,0:00:16.18,English,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Derek.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.89,0:00:16.18,Chinese,,0,0,0,,早啊  Derek
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.18,0:00:19.16,English,,0,0,0,,This car is all yours with no one up front.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.18,0:00:19.16,Chinese,,0,0,0,,本车由您独享  前排没有司机
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.16,0:00:22.73,English,,0,0,0,,- I really like the idea of fully autonomous vehicles,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.16,0:00:22.73,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我挺喜欢全自动驾驶汽车这个概念的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.73,0:00:26.76,English,,0,0,0,,but it's weird getting into a car with no driver
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.73,0:00:26.76,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但真正坐上没司机的汽车  任其驾驶  感觉还是怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.76,0:00:28.40,English,,0,0,0,,and just trusting the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.76,0:00:28.40,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但真正坐上没司机的汽车  任其驾驶  感觉还是怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.92,0:00:32.25,English,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna report back how this ride goes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.92,0:00:32.25,Chinese,,0,0,0,,待会我会分享一下  这一趟下来跑得怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.25,0:00:33.49,English,,0,0,0,,and how I feel about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.25,0:00:33.49,Chinese,,0,0,0,,以及我的一些感受
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.04,0:00:37.66,English,,0,0,0,,Oh, but full disclosure, this video is sponsored by Waymo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.04,0:00:37.66,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但是先说清楚  本视频由Waymo赞助
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.81,0:00:45.01,English,,0,0,0,,Start ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.81,0:00:45.01,Chinese,,0,0,0,,行程开始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.57,0:00:47.30,English,,0,0,0,,Ha ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.57,0:00:47.30,Chinese,,0,0,0,,哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.30,0:00:49.17,English,,0,0,0,,Make sure your seatbelt is fastened.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.30,0:00:49.17,Chinese,,0,0,0,,请系好您的安全带
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.17,0:00:53.90,English,,0,0,0,,For any questions, press the Help button to speak with a rider support agent.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.17,0:00:53.90,Chinese,,0,0,0,,如有任何问题  请按下帮助按钮来与客服通话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.90,0:00:54.92,English,,0,0,0,,- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.90,0:00:54.92,Chinese,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.92,0:00:56.62,English,,0,0,0,,Now let's see where we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.92,0:00:56.62,Chinese,,0,0,0,,现在看看我们往哪走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.62,0:00:59.50,English,,0,0,0,,It's looking at this car coming here. What's it gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.62,0:00:59.50,Chinese,,0,0,0,,那边来了一辆车 它会怎么应对呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.54,0:01:04.00,English,,0,0,0,,Oh, and it pulls in very smoothly behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.54,0:01:04.00,Chinese,,0,0,0,,哦  很丝滑地跟在它后面
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:06.40,English,,0,0,0,,No problems. Did not turn into traffic.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:06.40,Chinese,,0,0,0,,没问题  没堵塞交通
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.40,0:01:08.68,English,,0,0,0,,Waited until the car has went, and then it turned.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.40,0:01:08.68,Chinese,,0,0,0,,等到前面车走了才转弯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.42,0:01:10.06,English,,0,0,0,,I like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.42,0:01:10.06,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.33,0:01:14.28,English,,0,0,0,,I polled YouTube viewers about autonomous vehicles
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.33,0:01:14.28,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我在油管上开了一个自动驾驶汽车的投票
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.28,0:01:18.49,English,,0,0,0,,and half of you are excited and ready for them to be on the roads,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.28,0:01:18.49,Chinese,,0,0,0,,半数投票者很乐于尝试  认为这些车已经能上路了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.49,0:01:24.01,English,,0,0,0,,but over 40% said you thought the technology was still over 10 years away.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.49,0:01:24.01,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但逾四成人认为  真正的自动驾驶至少还得等10年
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.01,0:01:26.97,English,,0,0,0,,And for those people, I have news,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.01,0:01:26.97,Chinese,,0,0,0,,对这些悲观者  我可要告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.97,0:01:30.40,English,,0,0,0,,which is that, well, there is no driver in this car.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.97,0:01:30.40,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我现在坐的车已经没有司机了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.40,0:01:34.17,English,,0,0,0,,I'm currently inside a fully autonomous vehicle
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.40,0:01:34.17,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我正在乘坐一辆全自动驾驶的汽车
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.17,0:01:36.93,English,,0,0,0,,driving around a suburb of Phoenix, Arizona.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.17,0:01:36.93,Chinese,,0,0,0,,驰骋在亚利桑那州的凤凰城市郊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.86,0:01:39.93,English,,0,0,0,,Now I get that in some parts of the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.86,0:01:39.93,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我知道世界上还有一些
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.93,0:01:42.02,English,,0,0,0,,like, the roads aren't well enough maintained
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.93,0:01:42.02,Chinese,,0,0,0,,道路维护不足  司机也比较野的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.02,0:01:44.66,English,,0,0,0,,and people don't stay in their lane necessarily,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.02,0:01:44.66,Chinese,,0,0,0,,道路维护不足  司机也比较野的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.66,0:01:46.89,English,,0,0,0,,and so it'd be very hard for a computer to drive there,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.66,0:01:46.89,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这种情况  驾驶电脑可能还应付不来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.89,0:01:51.50,English,,0,0,0,,but at least under good conditions, the technology is currently functional.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.89,0:01:51.50,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但至少在较好的路况下  自动驾驶已经能用了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.82,0:02:02.50,English,,0,0,0,,- Now Waymo started out as the Google self-driving car project
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.82,0:02:02.50,Chinese,,0,0,0,,Waymo一开始是谷歌的自动驾驶项目
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.89,0:02:06.04,English,,0,0,0,,with what is possibly one of the cutest cars ever made.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.89,0:02:06.04,Chinese,,0,0,0,,用着可能是世界上最最可爱的车
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.57,0:02:12.78,English,,0,0,0,,I am inside the world's first fully autonomous vehicle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.57,0:02:12.78,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我现在坐在世界上第一辆全自动驾驶汽车里面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.78,0:02:17.77,English,,0,0,0,,Back in October 2015, this car went on a public road,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.78,0:02:17.77,Chinese,,0,0,0,,2015年10月  这辆车上了公开道路
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.77,0:02:22.21,English,,0,0,0,,ridden by Steve Mann, who has a disability, he is legally blind,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.77,0:02:22.21,Chinese,,0,0,0,,乘客 Steve Mann 是一位盲人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.21,0:02:25.21,English,,0,0,0,,but he could get around in this thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.21,0:02:25.21,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但他可以坐着这车到处转了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.21,0:02:28.58,English,,0,0,0,,which is affectionately known as the Firefly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.21,0:02:28.58,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这辆车被人们亲切地称为「萤火虫{\fsp-16}」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.58,0:02:32.32,English,,0,0,0,,This is such a simple vehicle. There's basically nothing in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.58,0:02:32.32,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这车真的超级精简  里面差不多啥都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.32,0:02:34.64,English,,0,0,0,,There's no steering wheel, no dashboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.32,0:02:34.64,Chinese,,0,0,0,,没有方向盘  没有仪表盘
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.64,0:02:36.17,English,,0,0,0,,This car is super basic.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.64,0:02:36.17,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这车太精简了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.17,0:02:37.81,English,,0,0,0,,There is no AC,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.17,0:02:37.81,Chinese,,0,0,0,,连空调都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.81,0:02:40.69,English,,0,0,0,,but there is an emergency stop button.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.81,0:02:40.69,Chinese,,0,0,0,,却有个紧急按钮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.10,0:02:43.10,English,,0,0,0,,That's my favorite button in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.10,0:02:43.10,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这车上我最喜欢这个按钮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.10,0:02:44.72,English,,0,0,0,,It reminds me of elevators.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.10,0:02:44.72,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这使我联想到了电梯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.72,0:02:46.59,English,,0,0,0,,You know, one of the important measures
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.59,0:02:48.73,English,,0,0,0,,that they had to put in automatic elevators
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.72,0:02:48.73,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你想 自动电梯里必定有的一样东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.73,0:02:51.10,English,,0,0,0,,was a big red stop button.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.73,0:02:51.10,Chinese,,0,0,0,,就是那个大大红红的停止按钮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.10,0:02:56.06,English,,0,0,0,,Did you know that before the 1940s, almost all elevators had drivers in them?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.10,0:02:56.06,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但你是否知道  在1940年以前  几乎每辆电梯都有司机
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.69,0:02:59.94,English,,0,0,0,,And when people started putting in driverless elevators,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.69,0:02:59.94,Chinese,,0,0,0,,后来当不用司机的电梯普及起来的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.32,0:03:02.12,English,,0,0,0,,well, the public was very concerned,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.12,0:03:03.89,English,,0,0,0,,and they didn't wanna ride in those elevators.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.32,0:03:03.89,Chinese,,0,0,0,,公众十分担心  他们不想坐这种电梯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.89,0:03:05.08,English,,0,0,0,,There was one guy who was like,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.89,0:03:05.08,Chinese,,0,0,0,,甚至还有个人说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.08,0:03:08.92,English,,0,0,0,,"I don't care if I have to walk up 12 flights of stairs for the rest of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.08,0:03:08.92,Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\fsp-16} {\fsp0}「我宁可后半辈子都走十二层楼梯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.92,0:03:10.52,English,,0,0,0,,I'm not taking that elevator."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.92,0:03:10.52,Chinese,,0,0,0,,也坚决不坐自动电梯{\fsp-16}」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.92,0:03:10.52,Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\an3\s1\fs54\pos(960,670)}真香{\s0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.52,0:03:11.57,English,,0,0,0,,And adoption was slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.52,0:03:11.57,Chinese,,0,0,0,,大众久久不能接纳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.57,0:03:15.39,English,,0,0,0,,I mean, they tried to advertise to help people understand that it was in fact safe,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.57,0:03:15.39,Chinese,,0,0,0,,制造商想尽办法让公众相信  自动电梯很安全
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.39,0:03:19.84,English,,0,0,0,,but, ultimately, there was an elevator drivers strike in New York City,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.39,0:03:19.84,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但最后  是纽约电梯司机的罢工彻底激怒了大众
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.84,0:03:21.78,English,,0,0,0,,and that really annoyed people,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.78,0:03:24.99,English,,0,0,0,,and it helped the adoption of automated elevators.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.84,0:03:24.99,Chinese,,0,0,0,,从而促使人们接受自动电梯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.21,0:03:27.38,English,,0,0,0,,If you found a driver in an elevator today,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.21,0:03:27.38,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你今天如果看到电梯里有个操纵员
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.38,0:03:29.71,English,,0,0,0,,you would wonder, "Why are they there?"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.38,0:03:29.71,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你肯定很迷惑 「这人是干啥的{\fsp-16}」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.05,0:03:32.64,English,,0,0,0,,Now you might think an elevator is just so simple,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.05,0:03:32.64,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你可能会说 电梯多简单啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.64,0:03:35.45,English,,0,0,0,,I mean, it is effectively one dimensional motion,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.64,0:03:35.45,Chinese,,0,0,0,,它不就只有一维运动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.45,0:03:40.30,English,,0,0,0,,but airplanes are also flown extensively by computers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.45,0:03:40.30,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但其实  飞机的大部分飞行工作也是计算机承担的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.06,0:03:47.15,English,,0,0,0,,I saw this particular landing where a plane is coming in into Vienna,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.06,0:03:47.15,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我见过一次  一架飞机来到了维也纳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.15,0:03:50.37,English,,0,0,0,,and it's just so foggy that the pilots can see almost nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.15,0:03:50.37,Chinese,,0,0,0,,雾很浓  飞行员能见度很低
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.37,0:03:52.63,English,,0,0,0,,I mean, this is the view from the cockpit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.37,0:03:52.63,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这是驾驶舱看到的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.18,0:03:57.83,English,,0,0,0,,and yet, they make a perfect, a textbook landing right on target.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.18,0:03:57.83,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但是他们完成了一次教科书级别的降落  正中跑道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.34,0:03:59.67,English,,0,0,0,,So how do they do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.34,0:03:59.67,Chinese,,0,0,0,,所以他们是咋做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.33,0:04:03.04,English,,0,0,0,,The answer is the pilots didn't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.33,0:04:03.04,Chinese,,0,0,0,,答案是  飞行员根本没操作
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.04,0:04:05.85,English,,0,0,0,,It was a CAT III autoland procedure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.04,0:04:05.85,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这是一个三类自动降落流程 （**REVIEW：抓个ACI的人来看看？**）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.85,0:04:10.03,English,,0,0,0,,The plane just came in and landed itself essentially.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.85,0:04:10.03,Chinese,,0,0,0,,飞机到了地点后  自动进场降落
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.03,0:04:11.85,English,,0,0,0,,Now, of course, the pilots are important
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.03,0:04:11.85,Chinese,,0,0,0,,诚然  飞行员也很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.85,0:04:15.51,English,,0,0,0,,and they're monitoring all of the instruments and controls,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.85,0:04:15.51,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他们要观察各个仪表和控制装置
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.51,0:04:19.78,English,,0,0,0,,but it's actually the plane and its computer getting the plane to land appropriately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.51,0:04:19.78,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但归根到底  是机上的计算机自己完成的完美降落
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.27,0:04:22.34,English,,0,0,0,,I was surprised to learn that
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.27,0:04:22.34,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我没想到的是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.34,0:04:28.03,English,,0,0,0,,humans are much more likely to take manual control and land on sunny days,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.34,0:04:28.03,Chinese,,0,0,0,,人们在晴朗的天气  更倾向于手动操作降落
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.03,0:04:30.13,English,,0,0,0,,like July 6th, 2013,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.03,0:04:30.13,Chinese,,0,0,0,,比如2013年7月6日
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.03,0:04:34.95,Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\an9}{\fs53.333}BV11s411R7rt / av3613944\N【ACI字幕组】空中浩劫S15：韩亚航空214号班机
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.42,0:04:34.95,English,,0,0,0,,when Asiana Airlines flight 214 was on final approach to San Francisco.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.42,0:04:34.95,Chinese,,0,0,0,,韩亚航空214号班机准备在旧金山机场降落
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.39,0:04:37.62,English,,0,0,0,,Attempting to manually land the plane,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.62,0:04:40.55,English,,0,0,0,,the pilot accidentally left the throttle at zero,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.39,0:04:40.55,Chinese,,0,0,0,,在手动降落的过程中  飞行员不小心把节流阀打到零了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.97,0:04:43.52,English,,0,0,0,,and by the time they realized and tried to abort the landing,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.97,0:04:43.52,Chinese,,0,0,0,,当他们意识到操作错误想要取消降落时
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.99,0:04:45.09,English,,0,0,0,,it was too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.99,0:04:45.09,Chinese,,0,0,0,,已为时已晚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.49,0:04:50.43,English,,0,0,0,,The plane crashed into the runway seawall and split in two.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.49,0:04:50.43,Chinese,,0,0,0,,飞机一头撞进跑道海堤 一分为二
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.14,0:04:54.33,English,,0,0,0,,Three people died in the aftermath of this accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.14,0:04:54.33,Chinese,,0,0,0,,三人在这场灾难中不幸丧生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.57,0:04:58.44,English,,0,0,0,,I think the counterintuitive thing is that
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.57,0:04:58.44,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我认为有个反直觉的事实是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.44,0:05:02.44,English,,0,0,0,,we expect the humans to be better, particularly in tough situations,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.44,0:05:02.44,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们认为  人类面对复杂情况时的表现相对会更好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.44,0:05:04.21,English,,0,0,0,,but when it comes to airplanes,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.21,0:05:08.32,English,,0,0,0,,if it's bad weather, you actually want the plane flying itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.44,0:05:08.32,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但在开飞机时  你反倒指望它在天气差的时候能自己飞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.84,0:05:11.62,English,,0,0,0,,So the obvious next question is,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.84,0:05:11.62,Chinese,,0,0,0,,很显然  下一个问题就是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.03,0:05:13.78,English,,0,0,0,,would you want the same thing for cars?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.03,0:05:13.78,Chinese,,0,0,0,,同样的事会发生在汽车上吗{\fsp-16}？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.34,0:05:17.56,English,,0,0,0,,There are all these different levels of autonomy
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.34,0:05:17.56,Chinese,,0,0,0,,汽车自动化被分为这些级别
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.56,0:05:20.81,English,,0,0,0,,and everything up to four requires a human driver
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.81,0:05:24.28,English,,0,0,0,,to be responsible and at the wheel at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.56,0:05:24.28,Chinese,,0,0,0,,四级 (L4) 以下的水平  都需要驾驶员持续观察和操作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.28,0:05:26.78,English,,0,0,0,,In the early days of the Google self-driving car project,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.28,0:05:26.78,Chinese,,0,0,0,,谷歌早期的自动驾驶汽车
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.11,0:05:29.52,English,,0,0,0,,they had a vehicle that was not yet level four,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.11,0:05:29.52,Chinese,,0,0,0,,并没有达到L4
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.52,0:05:31.60,English,,0,0,0,,so it still required a human driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.52,0:05:31.60,Chinese,,0,0,0,,因此需要驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.60,0:05:34.24,English,,0,0,0,,They let Google employees borrow the cars,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.60,0:05:34.24,Chinese,,0,0,0,,谷歌的员工可以借这些车来开
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.24,0:05:36.48,English,,0,0,0,,but they still had to be in control of the wheel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.24,0:05:36.48,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但是要手动操作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.83,0:05:38.49,English,,0,0,0,,And the volunteers were informed that
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.49,0:05:41.17,English,,0,0,0,,they were responsible for the car at all times
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.83,0:05:41.17,Chinese,,0,0,0,,志愿者们也被告知  他们开车时得对这辆车全权负责
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.17,0:05:44.36,English,,0,0,0,,and that they would be constantly recorded, like video recorded,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.36,0:05:45.63,English,,0,0,0,,while they were in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.17,0:05:45.63,Chinese,,0,0,0,,并且他们在车内时将会被持续录像
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.63,0:05:47.84,English,,0,0,0,,But still, within a short period of time,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.63,0:05:47.84,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但是没过多久
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.84,0:05:51.10,English,,0,0,0,,the engineers observed drivers rummaging around in their bags
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.84,0:05:51.10,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这些工程师就注意到驾驶员在包里翻翻找找
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.10,0:05:52.76,English,,0,0,0,,or checking phones,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.10,0:05:52.76,Chinese,,0,0,0,,刷手机
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.76,0:05:53.89,English,,0,0,0,,putting on makeup,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.76,0:05:53.89,Chinese,,0,0,0,,化妆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.89,0:05:56.98,English,,0,0,0,,or even sleeping in the driver's seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.89,0:05:56.98,Chinese,,0,0,0,,甚至坐在驾驶座上睡大觉zzz
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.46,0:06:00.57,English,,0,0,0,,All these drivers were trusting the technology too much,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.46,0:06:00.57,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这些司机对这个科技太过信任了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.57,0:06:03.11,English,,0,0,0,,which makes almost fully autonomous vehicles
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.11,0:06:06.17,English,,0,0,0,,potentially more dangerous than regular cars,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.57,0:06:06.17,Chinese,,0,0,0,,使得这些近乎全自动驾驶的汽车  可能会比普通的车要更危险
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.40,0:06:09.59,Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\an9}{\fs45}2020年6月1日\N台湾嘉义  特斯拉Model 3事故
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.17,0:06:09.59,English,,0,0,0,,I mean, if the driver is distracted or not prepared to take over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.17,0:06:09.59,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我指的是驾驶员分心了、没准备应对突发问题的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.17,0:06:14.31,English,,0,0,0,,So this is why Waymo decided that the only safe way to proceed is
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.17,0:06:14.31,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这就是为什么Waymo认为  唯一安全的方式是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.31,0:06:16.91,English,,0,0,0,,with a car that has at least level four autonomy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.31,0:06:16.91,Chinese,,0,0,0,,上路的自动驾驶汽车必须得达到L4级别
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.23,0:06:24.33,English,,0,0,0,,This is the depot where the cars go when they're not on the road,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.23,0:06:24.33,Chinese,,0,0,0,,还没用上的汽车就停在这个仓库
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.74,0:06:28.19,English,,0,0,0,,and it's also where people monitor all the rides in progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.74,0:06:28.19,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这里也有工作人员在监控所有正在进行的行程
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.89,0:06:30.40,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我的团队就坐这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.40,0:06:32.40,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你差不多可以看到有3支团队
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.72,0:06:35.30,Chinese,,0,0,0,,其中一支是我带的车队调度团队
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.30,0:06:41.08,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们每天都要分配驾驶任务  保障所有行程都能顺利完成
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.08,0:06:43.75,Chinese,,0,0,0,,然后是乘客支持团队  负责接听乘客的呼叫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.50,0:06:48.65,English,,0,0,0,,Thank you for calling the Waymo Rider Support.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.50,0:06:48.65,Chinese,,0,0,0,,Waymo司机支持团队感谢您的来电
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.65,0:06:50.62,English,,0,0,0,,This is Beulah, how can I help today?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.65,0:06:50.62,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我是比拉  请问您需要什么帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.62,0:06:53.53,English,,0,0,0,,- I just completed my ride, but I don't wanna get out of the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.63,0:06:53.53,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我刚跑完这趟行程  但我还想再多坐会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.53,0:06:54.84,English,,0,0,0,,I just wanna keep driving.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.53,0:06:54.84,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我想让它继续开
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.84,0:06:55.95,English,,0,0,0,,Is there a way that I can do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.84,0:06:55.95,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我能再设置行程吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.95,0:06:58.18,English,,0,0,0,,Right now, I don't see a trip started.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.95,0:06:58.18,Chinese,,0,0,0,,您目前暂时没有已开始的行程
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.18,0:07:00.78,English,,0,0,0,,Give me one moment here while I partner with my team, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.18,0:07:00.78,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我需要跟团队一同处理  请稍后
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.18,0:07:01.27,Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\an9}{\fs48}前方高亮警告
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.78,0:07:01.27,English,,0,0,0,,- Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.78,0:07:01.27,Chinese,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.44,0:07:10.26,English,,0,0,0,,Well, I just left all my stuff in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.44,0:07:10.26,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我的所有物品全丢车上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.16,0:07:12.16,English,,0,0,0,,I hope it comes back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.16,0:07:12.16,Chinese,,0,0,0,,希望这车能转回来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.91,0:07:24.35,English,,0,0,0,,- I think there's a lot of, still, resistance in terms of trusting the vehicle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.91,0:07:24.35,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我认为  要想信任自动驾驶  仍然有很多阻力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.35,0:07:29.05,English,,0,0,0,,And they ask you like, "How does it feel to be in a car without the driver?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.35,0:07:29.05,Chinese,,0,0,0,,人们会问你 「在没有司机的情况下  在车里的感觉如何{\fsp-16}」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.05,0:07:35.31,English,,0,0,0,,I was the first person to do public roads, fully driverless ride at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.05,0:07:35.31,Chinese,,0,0,0,,在公开道路上  我是在夜间进行全自动驾驶的第一人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.31,0:07:36.69,English,,0,0,0,,I always share the experience with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.31,0:07:36.69,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我一直和人们分享我的经历
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.69,0:07:39.57,English,,0,0,0,,It takes about two minutes for you to completely
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.57,0:07:42.16,English,,0,0,0,,forget that you are in a driverless vehicle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.69,0:07:42.16,Chinese,,0,0,0,,只要两分钟  你就能完全忘记自己坐着一辆没有司机的汽车
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.78,0:07:46.92,English,,0,0,0,,If the system really provides that feeling that you're safe
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.78,0:07:46.92,Chinese,,0,0,0,,如果系统能让你切实体会到安全感
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.92,0:07:48.89,English,,0,0,0,,and you see a couple of maneuvers,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.92,0:07:48.89,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你又看到车跑得很熟练
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.89,0:07:51.76,English,,0,0,0,,in less than two minutes, you're talking to whoever is next to you
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.89,0:07:51.76,Chinese,,0,0,0,,那不出两分钟  你就会跟旁边人开始唠嗑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.76,0:07:53.83,English,,0,0,0,,and not paying attention to what's happening anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.76,0:07:53.83,Chinese,,0,0,0,,不再关注驾驶情况
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.68,0:07:57.04,English,,0,0,0,,- Whoa,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.68,0:07:57.04,Chinese,,0,0,0,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.33,0:08:00.22,English,,0,0,0,,it doesn't make the indicator sound,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.33,0:08:00.22,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这车转向时没有“滴滴”声
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.22,0:08:03.63,English,,0,0,0,,so I just don't know when it's going to turn,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.22,0:08:03.63,Chinese,,0,0,0,,所以我（听声音）没法知道它啥时候会转弯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.31,0:08:06.30,English,,0,0,0,,but if I was watching the map, I would know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.31,0:08:06.30,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但我看地图就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.72,0:08:11.40,English,,0,0,0,,I think we have this bias to believe that
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.40,0:08:13.86,English,,0,0,0,,we're better at certain tasks than we actually are,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.72,0:08:13.86,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们常常会高估了自己处理特定任务的水平
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.33,0:08:16.89,English,,0,0,0,,like thinking that people are good at driving.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.33,0:08:16.89,Chinese,,0,0,0,,比如说  估计自己擅长开车
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.28,0:08:22.99,English,,0,0,0,,Surveys show 74% of people believe they are above average drivers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.28,0:08:22.99,Chinese,,0,0,0,,调查显示  74%的人认为自己的驾驶水平高于平均值
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.87,0:08:24.50,English,,0,0,0,,Think about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.87,0:08:24.50,Chinese,,0,0,0,,可想而知
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.20,0:08:28.55,English,,0,0,0,,In the 20th century, 60 million people were killed on the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.20,0:08:28.55,Chinese,,0,0,0,,在20世纪  有六千万人死于交通事故
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.55,0:08:31.77,English,,0,0,0,,That's basically an extra world war's worth of deaths.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.55,0:08:31.77,Chinese,,0,0,0,,死亡人数相当于又打了一场世界大战
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.29,0:08:34.70,English,,0,0,0,,And we really have no one to blame but ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.29,0:08:34.70,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但我们只能怪自己
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.97,0:08:37.57,English,,0,0,0,,The National Transportation and Safety Board has identified
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.97,0:08:37.57,Chinese,,0,0,0,,国家运输安全委员会 (NTSB) 得出结论 *高亮警告
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.57,0:08:41.04,English,,0,0,0,,human error as the cause of 94% of accidents.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.57,0:08:41.04,Chinese,,0,0,0,,94%的交通事故是人为错误造成的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.49,0:08:45.14,English,,0,0,0,,Most of these errors are impossible for a machine to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.49,0:08:45.14,Chinese,,0,0,0,,绝大多数这类错误是机器不可能犯的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.19,0:08:51.25,English,,0,0,0,,Every year when people are backing out of driveways or parking spaces,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.25,0:08:54.60,English,,0,0,0,,in the U.S, up to 200 people are killed,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.19,0:08:54.60,Chinese,,0,0,0,,在美国  每年死于倒车事故的人多达200人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.60,0:08:58.76,English,,0,0,0,,and it's frequently older people or children, the children of the drivers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.60,0:08:58.76,Chinese,,0,0,0,,死者多为老人和小孩  司机的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.38,0:09:00.57,English,,0,0,0,,It's awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.38,0:09:00.57,Chinese,,0,0,0,,太糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.57,0:09:03.97,English,,0,0,0,,And it comes down to the fact that we don't have eyes in the back of our head,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.57,0:09:03.97,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这归根到底是因为  我们毕竟没在后脑勺长眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.97,0:09:07.35,English,,0,0,0,,and even the backup cameras still have blind spots.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.97,0:09:07.35,Chinese,,0,0,0,,即使是倒车雷达  也免不了存在盲区
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.35,0:09:13.25,English,,0,0,0,,But if you have a vehicle that has lidar, and radar, and 29 cameras,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.35,0:09:13.25,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但如果你的车子上有激光雷达、微波雷达  还有29个摄像头
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.25,0:09:16.40,English,,0,0,0,,you're just not going to hit them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.25,0:09:16.40,Chinese,,0,0,0,,那就不会再碰上后面的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.40,0:09:21.06,English,,0,0,0,,Up here in the very prominent top, there is a 360 lidar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.40,0:09:21.06,Chinese,,0,0,0,,在车顶上有个硕大的360°激光雷达
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.49,0:09:23.76,English,,0,0,0,,So it can see all around the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.49,0:09:23.76,Chinese,,0,0,0,,它对周遭事物能一览无余
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.76,0:09:26.95,English,,0,0,0,,It can see up to 300 meters away with a lidar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.76,0:09:26.95,Chinese,,0,0,0,,激光雷达能识别到300米外的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.32,0:09:32.09,English,,0,0,0,,The way the lidar works is it shoots out invisible laser beams,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.32,0:09:32.09,Chinese,,0,0,0,,激光雷达的工作原理是  发射肉眼不可见的激光束
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.09,0:09:35.04,English,,0,0,0,,scanning around millions of times a second,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.09,0:09:35.04,Chinese,,0,0,0,,每秒扫描周围百万次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.04,0:09:37.05,English,,0,0,0,,and then it detects the reflection,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.04,0:09:37.05,Chinese,,0,0,0,,它会探测反射的激光
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.05,0:09:38.99,English,,0,0,0,,and how long it takes to come back
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.99,0:09:41.72,English,,0,0,0,,allows you to determine how far it is to that object.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.05,0:09:41.72,Chinese,,0,0,0,,计算激光来回的时间  即可知道外部事物距车有多远
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.14,0:09:46.57,English,,0,0,0,,So what it's doing is like painting a 3D picture of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.14,0:09:46.57,Chinese,,0,0,0,,它所做的就好比是给环境画了张三维的画
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.08,0:09:50.99,English,,0,0,0,,There are 29 cameras around this vehicle,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.08,0:09:50.99,Chinese,,0,0,0,,车子全身有29个摄像头
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.99,0:09:53.50,English,,0,0,0,,which gives you full 360 vision.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.99,0:09:53.50,Chinese,,0,0,0,,提供了360°全方位的视野
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.50,0:09:56.79,English,,0,0,0,,It gives you close range vision, what is right next to the car,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.50,0:09:56.79,Chinese,,0,0,0,,它能看得近  近到紧挨着车子的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.79,0:10:01.09,English,,0,0,0,,and also long range vision, going out 500 meters.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.79,0:10:01.09,Chinese,,0,0,0,,也能看到远到500米外的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.09,0:10:05.61,English,,0,0,0,,This car could detect a stop sign or a pedestrian 500 meters away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.09,0:10:05.61,Chinese,,0,0,0,,它能识别出500米外的停车路牌和行人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.61,0:10:08.57,English,,0,0,0,,How many of us have eyesight that is that good?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.61,0:10:08.57,Chinese,,0,0,0,,没几个地球人有这么好的视力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.57,0:10:11.53,English,,0,0,0,,There is also a microphone up on top
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.57,0:10:11.53,Chinese,,0,0,0,,顶上还有个麦克风
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.11,0:10:14.65,English,,0,0,0,,to listen to what's happening in the environment,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.11,0:10:14.65,Chinese,,0,0,0,,来倾听周围环境发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.65,0:10:19.38,English,,0,0,0,,and if there are sirens, then the car will pull over to the side of the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.65,0:10:19.38,Chinese,,0,0,0,,如果有警笛声  车子会靠边停
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.38,0:10:22.26,English,,0,0,0,,It's gotta be able to respond to emergency vehicles.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.38,0:10:22.26,Chinese,,0,0,0,,它能够对应急车种有所反应
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.56,0:10:35.35,English,,0,0,0,,What I wanna see here is, how does it handle a parking lot
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.56,0:10:35.35,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我想看看它如何应对停车场的环境
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.04,0:10:40.21,English,,0,0,0,,where there's people driving in unusual ways and
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.04,0:10:40.21,Chinese,,0,0,0,,停车场里的开车方式不同于道路
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.21,0:10:42.21,English,,0,0,0,,possibly pedestrians walking around?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.21,0:10:42.21,Chinese,,0,0,0,,并且会有行人到处走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.15,0:10:47.64,English,,0,0,0,,Whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.15,0:10:47.64,Chinese,,0,0,0,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.17,0:10:49.79,English,,0,0,0,,That was a sudden stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.17,0:10:49.79,Chinese,,0,0,0,,来了个急停
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.04,0:10:53.73,English,,0,0,0,,The car made a pretty hard stop there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.04,0:10:53.73,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这刹车怕是踩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.73,0:10:57.58,English,,0,0,0,,I think it saw that guy with a cart coming up on a pedestrian crosswalk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.73,0:10:57.58,Chinese,,0,0,0,,它应该看到了那个推车的人走到了人行横道上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.95,0:11:01.43,English,,0,0,0,,And one of the interesting things that the vehicle is always doing is
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.95,0:11:01.43,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这辆车一直在用一种有趣的驾驶方式
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.43,0:11:04.43,English,,0,0,0,,not only seeing where things are and where they're going,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.43,0:11:04.43,Chinese,,0,0,0,,它不单单看到事物在哪里，在往哪边移动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.43,0:11:08.15,English,,0,0,0,,but also making predictions about where they're likely to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.43,0:11:08.15,Chinese,,0,0,0,,它还会预测事物最有可能往哪边移动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.15,0:11:12.24,English,,0,0,0,,So this car doesn't just have one potential future.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.15,0:11:12.24,Chinese,,0,0,0,,所以这车并非一定会刹停  也可能有其他反应
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.24,0:11:15.96,English,,0,0,0,,It's constantly imagining, "Well, he might cross at the crosswalk,"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.24,0:11:15.96,Chinese,,0,0,0,,它不断地想象 「嗯  他可能会在人行横道上过马路{\fsp-16}」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.96,0:11:18.68,English,,0,0,0,,or, "He might keep going," or, "He might turn left,"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.96,0:11:18.68,Chinese,,0,0,0,,或者「他可能会继续走」或者「他可能会左转{\fsp-16}」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.68,0:11:22.16,English,,0,0,0,,and so it has to be prepared for all of those different options.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.68,0:11:22.16,Chinese,,0,0,0,,它得对这多种可能统统做好准备
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.16,0:11:24.08,English,,0,0,0,,And it even weights the options
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.16,0:11:24.08,Chinese,,0,0,0,,它还会衡量各种选项的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.08,0:11:27.10,English,,0,0,0,,of like how likely it thinks that he's gonna go on the crosswalk
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.08,0:11:27.10,Chinese,,0,0,0,,比如说  这人有多大可能上人行横道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.10,0:11:29.03,English,,0,0,0,,versus go straight versus turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.10,0:11:29.03,Chinese,,0,0,0,,又有多大可能直走或者左转
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.39,0:11:31.79,English,,0,0,0,,And you can see that with the thickness of the line
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.79,0:11:34.31,English,,0,0,0,,in the little simulated graphic that they have.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.39,0:11:34.31,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这在他们的模拟图像中以线条粗细的方式来体现
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.49,0:11:41.29,English,,0,0,0,,A few years back, I think a lot of people were talking about
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.49,0:11:41.29,Chinese,,0,0,0,,几年前有很多人在讨论
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.29,0:11:46.16,English,,0,0,0,,how autonomous vehicles have to figure out who to hit in case of an accident,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.29,0:11:46.16,Chinese,,0,0,0,,发生事故时  自动驾驶汽车要如何抉择该撞谁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.16,0:11:49.04,English,,0,0,0,,like do the pick the orphan or the nun?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.16,0:11:49.04,Chinese,,0,0,0,,要撞孤儿还是修女（**REVIEW：不知道是不是俗语**）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.83,0:12:05.43,Chinese,,0,0,0,,{\an1}{\fs48}{\pos(199,598)}{\fad(500,0)}{\c&000000&}{\shad0}{\bord0}{\b1}无人驾驶汽车混乱的伦理{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.04,0:11:51.63,English,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Should the car hit the motorcyclist with the helmet on
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.04,0:11:51.63,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这车是应该撞右边带了头盔的摩托车手…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.63,0:11:53.91,English,,0,0,0,,{\an8}because his injuries might be less severe
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.63,0:11:53.91,Chinese,,0,0,0,,因为他受的伤不会那么重呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.91,0:11:56.87,English,,0,0,0,,{\an8}or should the car hit the motorcyclist who does not have a helmet on
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.91,0:11:56.87,Chinese,,0,0,0,,还是应该撞左边没带头盔的摩托车手…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.87,0:11:58.97,English,,0,0,0,,{\an8}because he did not properly protect himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.87,0:11:58.97,Chinese,,0,0,0,,因为他没有好好保护自己{\fsp-16}？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.97,0:12:01.80,English,,0,0,0,,{\an8}If cars were programmed to hit the motorcyclist with the helmet,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.97,0:12:01.80,Chinese,,0,0,0,,如果这车的程序被设定为  去撞戴了安全帽的车手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.80,0:12:05.43,English,,0,0,0,,{\an8}that would mean that, in a way, it would become safer to ride without a helmet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.80,0:12:05.43,Chinese,,0,0,0,,那从某种意义上来说  不带安全帽的车手反而更安全了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.31,0:12:11.70,English,,0,0,0,,But the reality is that 99% of accidents aren't like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.31,0:12:11.70,Chinese,,0,0,0,,可在现实中  99%的事故都不是这样的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.70,0:12:16.85,English,,0,0,0,,Every year, around 1.3 million people are killed on the roads,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.70,0:12:16.85,Chinese,,0,0,0,,每一年  大约有130万人死于交通事故
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.85,0:12:19.17,English,,0,0,0,,almost all of them due to human error.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.85,0:12:19.17,Chinese,,0,0,0,,绝大部分都是人为失误导致
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.17,0:12:22.25,English,,0,0,0,,If autonomous cars can reduce these fatalities,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.17,0:12:22.25,Chinese,,0,0,0,,如果自动驾驶汽车能够减少事故死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.25,0:12:25.74,English,,0,0,0,,then the real moral dilemma is not getting them on the road sooner
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.25,0:12:25.74,Chinese,,0,0,0,,那么真正导致这些车没法上路的道德困境在于
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.74,0:12:28.37,English,,0,0,0,,for fear we haven't worked out exactly how they'll react
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.74,0:12:28.37,Chinese,,0,0,0,,因为我们惧怕车在极小概率情况下的反应尚未清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.37,0:12:32.11,English,,0,0,0,,to extremely unlikely hypothetical scenarios.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.37,0:12:32.11,Chinese,,0,0,0,,因为我们惧怕车在极小概率情况下的反应尚未清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.44,0:12:36.33,English,,0,0,0,,I think humans are becoming worse drivers
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.44,0:12:36.33,Chinese,,0,0,0,,人类正在成为更差的司机
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.33,0:12:38.90,English,,0,0,0,,because we're just so prone to distraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.33,0:12:38.90,Chinese,,0,0,0,,因为我们真的太容易分心了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.71,0:12:44.24,English,,0,0,0,,Think about the main reasons why cars crash:
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.71,0:12:44.24,Chinese,,0,0,0,,想想撞车的主要原因
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.24,0:12:49.74,English,,0,0,0,,because people are speeding, they're under the influence, they're distracted.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.24,0:12:49.74,Chinese,,0,0,0,,就是人们超速了、受到什么影响了、分心了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.22,0:12:55.35,English,,0,0,0,,I mean, these sorts of problems, an autonomous vehicle would not have.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.22,0:12:55.35,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我认为这些问题都是自动驾驶汽车不会有的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.35,0:12:57.39,English,,0,0,0,,You don't get a distracted driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.35,0:12:57.39,Chinese,,0,0,0,,电脑“司机”永远不会分心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.39,0:12:58.74,English,,0,0,0,,The ultimate question, right,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.74,0:13:02.09,English,,0,0,0,,that everyone wants to know, that I want to know the answer to is,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.39,0:13:02.09,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这个终极问题的答案  也是我和所有人都想知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.09,0:13:05.80,English,,0,0,0,,as these vehicles stand, are they better than the average human?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.09,0:13:05.80,Chinese,,0,0,0,,就目前的自动驾驶水平而言  它们是否优于人类的平均水平
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.80,0:13:08.61,English,,0,0,0,,Not than the best human, but just like an average human.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.80,0:13:08.61,Chinese,,0,0,0,,不和最好的比  但能不能达到普通人的水平
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.61,0:13:12.38,English,,0,0,0,,Like replacing some random car on the street with one of these vehicles,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.61,0:13:12.38,Chinese,,0,0,0,,比如说随机把大街上的一些车换成自动驾驶汽车
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.38,0:13:13.83,English,,0,0,0,,does that make the road safer?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.38,0:13:13.83,Chinese,,0,0,0,,会让这条路更安全吗{\fsp-16}？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.83,0:13:14.89,English,,0,0,0,,- Yes, it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.83,0:13:14.89,Chinese,,0,0,0,,答案是肯定的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.89,0:13:19.86,English,,0,0,0,,I think we would never launch a rider-only service
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.89,0:13:19.86,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我想  如果一个没有司机的乘车服务不满足基础的安全框架
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.86,0:13:23.27,English,,0,0,0,,if we did not meet that base safety framework.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.86,0:13:23.27,Chinese,,0,0,0,,那我们坚决不会向大众推行这项服务
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.27,0:13:26.33,English,,0,0,0,,- If that's true, it means like
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.27,0:13:26.33,Chinese,,0,0,0,,如果这是真的，这就意味着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.33,0:13:31.30,English,,0,0,0,,every vehicle that's not on the road is kind of a worse situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.33,0:13:31.30,Chinese,,0,0,0,,所有不在路上的车都处于更糟糕的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.30,0:13:31.96,English,,0,0,0,,do you know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.30,0:13:31.96,Chinese,,0,0,0,,懂我意思吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.96,0:13:35.29,English,,0,0,0,,- We are really working really hard to launch this
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.29,0:13:38.41,English,,0,0,0,,in larger areas and new areas too,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.96,0:13:38.41,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们真的在想尽办法  往更广阔的领域提供自动驾驶服务
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.41,0:13:39.75,English,,0,0,0,,but we need to have the experience
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.41,0:13:39.75,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但我们需要更多的实践经验
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.75,0:13:42.38,English,,0,0,0,,to show the regulators why we believe it's safer,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.75,0:13:42.38,Chinese,,0,0,0,,来向监管机构证明「我们相信它更安全」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.38,0:13:45.12,English,,0,0,0,,and, for that, you need to be driving miles,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.38,0:13:45.12,Chinese,,0,0,0,,为此需要更多的行驶里程
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.12,0:13:50.12,English,,0,0,0,,a number of miles that you feel comfortable with, statistically speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.12,0:13:50.12,Chinese,,0,0,0,,从统计学角度来说要多到让人足够放心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.12,0:13:54.44,English,,0,0,0,,- These vehicles have way more experience than any human driver
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.12,0:13:54.44,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这些车的驾驶经验比任何一位人类老司机都多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.44,0:13:56.26,English,,0,0,0,,because they've now accumulated data
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.26,0:14:00.22,English,,0,0,0,,over 20 million miles of driving on public roads.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.44,0:14:00.22,Chinese,,0,0,0,,因为他们在公共道路上收集的行驶数据  已超过两千万英里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.73,0:14:05.22,English,,0,0,0,,If you were an average driver, you'd have to drive for a thousand years
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.22,0:14:07.09,English,,0,0,0,,to accumulate that sort of experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.73,0:14:07.09,Chinese,,0,0,0,,普通司机需要开上一千年的车  才能积累这么多里程
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.09,0:14:11.88,English,,0,0,0,,And all of that experience can be used to train the systems, to fix the software,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.09,0:14:11.88,Chinese,,0,0,0,,Waymo积累的所有经验都可用于训练系统、修正软件
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.88,0:14:14.29,English,,0,0,0,,and used across all the vehicles in the fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.88,0:14:14.29,Chinese,,0,0,0,,然后广泛应用于所有现行车辆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.73,0:14:18.90,English,,0,0,0,,In 2019, Waymo released a study of its data,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.73,0:14:18.90,Chinese,,0,0,0,,在2019年  Waymo发布了一份数据研究报告
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.90,0:14:21.91,English,,0,0,0,,over 6.1 million miles of automated driving
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.91,0:14:24.26,English,,0,0,0,,in the Phoenix, Arizona metropolitan area.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.90,0:14:24.26,Chinese,,0,0,0,,基于超过610万英里的  在凤凰城都市圈的自动驾驶路试
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.60,0:14:27.66,English,,0,0,0,,Of the 18 total accidents that occurred during the study,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.60,0:14:27.66,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这次研究总计发生了18起事故  在这些事故中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.66,0:14:31.20,English,,0,0,0,,none were serious enough to expect significant injury or death.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.66,0:14:31.20,Chinese,,0,0,0,,没有一项是严重到会导致重大伤亡的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.53,0:14:32.78,English,,0,0,0,,In Waymo's Safety Report,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.53,0:14:32.78,Chinese,,0,0,0,,在Waymo的安全报告中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.78,0:14:35.42,English,,0,0,0,,they found some types of accidents have been
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.42,0:14:39.33,English,,0,0,0,,completely eliminated by this autonomous driving system,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.78,0:14:39.33,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他们发现  自动驾驶系统已让某些类型的事故不复存在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.33,0:14:42.08,English,,0,0,0,,like the car doesn't go off the road
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.33,0:14:42.08,Chinese,,0,0,0,,车子不会驶离道路
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.08,0:14:44.09,English,,0,0,0,,and it doesn't hit stationary objects.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.08,0:14:44.09,Chinese,,0,0,0,,也不会撞击静止物体
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.68,0:14:47.05,English,,0,0,0,,Humans, humans do those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.68,0:14:47.05,Chinese,,0,0,0,,人类才会犯这种错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.82,0:14:52.70,English,,0,0,0,,If you look at the eight significant accidents that happened with Waymo vehicles
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.70,0:14:55.42,English,,0,0,0,,over the six million miles of driving,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.82,0:14:55.42,Chinese,,0,0,0,,至于他们这600万英里的行驶中  发生的八起重大安全事故
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.82,0:14:58.90,English,,0,0,0,,all eight of them involve a human driver
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.90,0:15:01.07,English,,0,0,0,,of another vehicle doing something stupid,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.82,0:15:01.07,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这些事故都涉及到  另一辆车有个不守交规的人类司机
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.07,0:15:03.40,English,,0,0,0,,like driving on the wrong side of the road
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.07,0:15:03.40,Chinese,,0,0,0,,比如  逆行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.40,0:15:04.90,English,,0,0,0,,or running a red light
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.40,0:15:04.90,Chinese,,0,0,0,,闯红灯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.90,0:15:06.84,English,,0,0,0,,or going through a stop sign
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.90,0:15:06.84,Chinese,,0,0,0,,看到停止路牌却不停车
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.84,0:15:07.80,English,,0,0,0,,or failing to yield
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.84,0:15:07.80,Chinese,,0,0,0,,让路失败
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.80,0:15:10.59,English,,0,0,0,,or going 20 miles per hour over the speed limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.80,0:15:10.59,Chinese,,0,0,0,,超速  比上限高了每小时20英里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.59,0:15:15.09,English,,0,0,0,,There were three incidents involving Waymo vehicles and pedestrians,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.59,0:15:15.09,Chinese,,0,0,0,,有三起事故的当事双方是Waymo的车辆和行人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.82,0:15:19.74,English,,0,0,0,,but in all three, the Waymo vehicle was stationary
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.82,0:15:19.74,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但在这三起事故中  Waymo的车都是静止的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.18,0:15:24.79,English,,0,0,0,,and the pedestrian or cyclist/skateboarder ran into the vehicle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.18,0:15:24.79,Chinese,,0,0,0,,是行人、自行车手、滑板者撞向车辆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.88,0:15:29.29,English,,0,0,0,,Waymo also takes some of that real-world data
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.88,0:15:29.29,Chinese,,0,0,0,,Waymo也采集了一些真实世界数据
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.66,0:15:31.83,English,,0,0,0,,and they put it into simulations
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.66,0:15:31.83,Chinese,,0,0,0,,放进了模拟系统中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.18,0:15:33.45,English,,0,0,0,,and they tweak it a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.18,0:15:33.45,Chinese,,0,0,0,,并稍微调整了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.45,0:15:37.16,English,,0,0,0,,So they try adding like a bicyclist going fast or going slow,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.45,0:15:37.16,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他们试着加入一个骑得很快或者很慢的自行车手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.16,0:15:39.43,English,,0,0,0,,or they make the car turn faster or slower.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.16,0:15:39.43,Chinese,,0,0,0,,或者让车加速或减速
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.73,0:15:42.65,English,,0,0,0,,So they change all these parameters and variables,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.73,0:15:42.65,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他们更改这些参数与变量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.65,0:15:44.88,English,,0,0,0,,and they see what the software will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.65,0:15:44.88,Chinese,,0,0,0,,观察程序会如何应对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.88,0:15:49.52,English,,0,0,0,,And they've trained the software on an additional 20 billion miles of driving,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.52,0:15:51.72,English,,0,0,0,,not on the road but in the simulation,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.88,0:15:51.72,Chinese,,0,0,0,,他们额外投入了200亿英里的模拟里程去训练程序
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.72,0:15:55.09,English,,0,0,0,,so that's a thousand times more experience again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.72,0:15:55.09,Chinese,,0,0,0,,所以这又多了成千倍的经验
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.64,0:15:58.35,English,,0,0,0,,The question for me is,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.64,0:15:58.35,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我的问题是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.85,0:16:01.74,English,,0,0,0,,when is stepping inside an autonomous car
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.85,0:16:01.74,Chinese,,0,0,0,,等到什么时候  坐上自动驾驶汽车的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.74,0:16:04.60,English,,0,0,0,,gonna feel the same as stepping inside an elevator?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.74,0:16:04.60,Chinese,,0,0,0,,才能无异于坐电梯的感觉{\fsp-16}？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.58,0:16:08.53,English,,0,0,0,,Because I think that time may be coming sooner than you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.58,0:16:08.53,Chinese,,0,0,0,,因为我觉得  这个时刻会比你们想像的来得更快
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.11,0:16:10.63,English,,0,0,0,,I like the idea of this technology,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.11,0:16:10.63,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我喜欢这个技术点子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.63,0:16:14.41,English,,0,0,0,,but, honestly, getting in the car, I wasn't quite sure how I would feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.63,0:16:14.41,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但说实话  刚坐上这车时  我不知道我会有个啥体验
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.41,0:16:15.97,English,,0,0,0,,I was a little bit uncertain,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.41,0:16:15.97,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我一开始还不太肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.97,0:16:19.20,English,,0,0,0,,but once I saw.. it just handles so confidently...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.97,0:16:19.20,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但等我看到  它开起来如此驾轻就熟之后…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.20,0:16:20.82,English,,0,0,0,,Like driving is one of those things that I feel like
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.82,0:16:22.67,English,,0,0,0,,you can't hide whether you're a good or bad driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.20,0:16:22.67,Chinese,,0,0,0,,开车这种东西嘛  水平是骡子是马一遛就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.67,0:16:24.83,English,,0,0,0,,It's just like, "Oh, what's gonna happen when
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.83,0:16:28.04,English,,0,0,0,,there's a parked car or a cyclist or a pedestrian,"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.67,0:16:28.04,Chinese,,0,0,0,,比如说  如果那里停着辆车、有个人骑单车或者步行会怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.04,0:16:32.10,English,,0,0,0,,and it just sort of handles all those situations with such confidence and ease
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.04,0:16:32.10,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这车能如此从容自信、驾轻就熟地处理所有这些情况
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.10,0:16:34.50,English,,0,0,0,,that I think I stopped thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.10,0:16:34.50,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我觉得我不必再担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.50,0:16:36.92,English,,0,0,0,,- After they pass a couple of your mental tests,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.50,0:16:36.92,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你在内心里给它打分通过之后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.92,0:16:39.66,English,,0,0,0,,you're like, "I'm good. I think I can.. I'll be okay."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.92,0:16:39.66,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你会觉得「我可以  我觉得…  我应该没事{\fsp-24}」{\fsp0}（笑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.01,0:16:41.86,English,,0,0,0,,- Yeah, yeah, I felt the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.01,0:16:41.86,Chinese,,0,0,0,,对  我也是这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.86,0:16:45.37,English,,0,0,0,,I think a lot of people miss the bigger implications of what is achievable
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.86,0:16:45.37,Chinese,,0,0,0,,许多人意识不到  等到全自动驾驶真正普及之时
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.37,0:16:48.08,English,,0,0,0,,once fully autonomous driving is commonplace.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.37,0:16:48.08,Chinese,,0,0,0,,究竟能产生多么深远的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.08,0:16:52.60,English,,0,0,0,,Riders with disabilities, seniors, and the blind can get around more easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.08,0:16:52.60,Chinese,,0,0,0,,残疾人、老年人、盲人乘客出行会方便得多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.60,0:16:54.31,English,,0,0,0,,Transportation will get cheaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.60,0:16:54.31,Chinese,,0,0,0,,运输会越来越便宜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.60,0:17:00.23,English,,0,0,0,,Think of all the wasted value in the cars that spend over 95% of their time parked.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.60,0:17:00.23,Chinese,,0,0,0,,想想那些每天上路时间不超过5%的车  浪费了多少资源
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.23,0:17:03.28,English,,0,0,0,,We can regain a bunch of time and feel happier
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.23,0:17:03.28,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们可以重新利用这些时间变得更快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.28,0:17:06.73,English,,0,0,0,,because commuting and being stuck in traffic sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.28,0:17:06.73,Chinese,,0,0,0,,因为上下班还堵车糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.40,0:17:11.82,English,,0,0,0,,We can reduce traffic because vehicles will have better awareness of each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.40,0:17:11.82,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们可以减少交通堵塞  因为车子会更了解彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.82,0:17:14.91,English,,0,0,0,,You can imagine one day when all the cars are fully autonomous,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.82,0:17:14.91,Chinese,,0,0,0,,可以想象  有朝一日  路上的所有车都是全自动驾驶的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.91,0:17:18.53,English,,0,0,0,,they can execute a beautiful ballet driving together,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.91,0:17:18.53,Chinese,,0,0,0,,往来车辆可以交织通行  像芭蕾舞一样优雅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.53,0:17:21.19,English,,0,0,0,,and when that time comes, we can eliminate parking lots
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.53,0:17:21.19,Chinese,,0,0,0,,等那一天真正到来之时  我们将再也不需要停车场
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.19,0:17:23.39,English,,0,0,0,,and add green spaces to our cities.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.19,0:17:23.39,Chinese,,0,0,0,,给城市节省出了更多的绿化空间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.70,0:17:26.42,English,,0,0,0,,And, most importantly, widespread adoption of autonomous cars
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.70,0:17:26.42,Chinese,,0,0,0,,最重要的是  全自动驾驶汽车的普及
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.42,0:17:29.96,English,,0,0,0,,could prevent tens of thousands of fatalities in the U.S. alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.42,0:17:29.96,Chinese,,0,0,0,,光是在美国  就能避免数以万计的交通事故
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.50,0:17:33.08,English,,0,0,0,,When do you think that this will be a reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.50,0:17:33.08,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你什么时候会觉得这会成为现实
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.08,0:17:35.11,English,,0,0,0,,like, clearly it's coming, but when?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.08,0:17:35.11,Chinese,,0,0,0,,显然这一切快来了  但具体是啥时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.11,0:17:37.04,English,,0,0,0,,- Yeah. If you're talking about big cities,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.11,0:17:37.04,Chinese,,0,0,0,,如果你说的是大城市
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.04,0:17:40.70,English,,0,0,0,,I'm hoping the next five years will be really game changing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.04,0:17:40.70,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我希望接下来的五年的变化将会很大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.70,0:17:41.37,English,,0,0,0,,- I'm excited to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.70,0:17:41.37,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我很期待能亲眼看到
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.37,0:17:45.15,English,,0,0,0,,- Me too, believe me. Believe me. I just don't want to commute to work anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.37,0:17:45.15,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我也一样  相信我  我真的不想再开车上班了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.15,0:17:46.48,English,,0,0,0,,I would love to sit in the backseat,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.48,0:17:48.69,English,,0,0,0,,do my work on the way there and on the way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.15,0:17:48.69,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我会爱上坐在后座  在来回的路上做我的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.78,0:17:51.34,English,,0,0,0,,- Or do something fun, watch a movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.78,0:17:51.34,Chinese,,0,0,0,,或者做点什么有意思的  比如看看电影
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.34,0:17:52.60,English,,0,0,0,,- Or sleep, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.34,0:17:52.60,Chinese,,0,0,0,,或者睡觉（笑
